<![CDATA[<font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="font-family: arial;"><font style=""><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Hi {!Target_User.FirstName},</span><br style=""><br style=""><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">You have been granted access to&nbsp;</span></font></font><span style="font-family: arial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Internal Idea Exchange</span><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="font-family: arial;"><font style="">.<br style=""><br style=""></font></font><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="">The Internal Idea Exchange is a feedback platform where Illumina employees can propose solutions or enhancements. Ideas should exemplify the voice of the customer or voice of the field teams and are then voted on by other members to drive idea awareness. Ideas are reviewed quarterly by the Voice of Customer team (or more frequently for some Categories) and will advance to the correct Project Management Teams (PMT) for implementation. These ideas are centralized, crowd-sourced, and inform data-driven project prioritization.</font><span style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; margin: 0in;"><br></p><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="font-family: arial;"><font style=""><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">To get started,&nbsp;</span></font></font><span style="font-family: arial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">please visit Internal Idea Exchange via Innovation Hub/Ideas(Innohub) app in Salesforce.&nbsp;</span><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="font-family: arial;"><font style=""><br style=""><br style=""><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Feel free to contact&nbsp;</span></font></font><sp